{"tid":2329412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華屢制裁澳貨 五眼聯盟擬報復","createTime":"2020-12-17T08:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T08:39:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"249f2508b1a292ffd294c741f153fd03ca8d3622","tid":2329412,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:23:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201217/DK7Y7HGDGBHFTFVXLYERSNNTE4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201217%2FDK7Y7HGDGBHFTFVXLYERSNNTE4%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28Qpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=934d545f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201217%2FDK7Y7HGDGBHFTFVXLYERSNNTE4%2F&h=111d5375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201217/DK7Y7HGDGBHFTFVXLYERSNNTE4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華屢制裁澳貨 五眼聯盟擬報復<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FVZ7_XIwZhUwmWUDe-AeeQVtFa4=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F24QSOCRJJDMRKNNGB5KUWSVCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFVZ7_XIwZhUwmWUDe-AeeQVtFa4%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF24QSOCRJJDMRKNNGB5KUWSVCA.jpg&h=d9e7f913&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■澳洲正式向世貿控告中國發動貿易戰。<br />\n<br />\n中國近日不斷出招向澳洲貿易施壓，澳洲傳媒報道，由澳洲、新西蘭、美國、加拿大、英國組成的「五眼聯盟」正在商議一項計劃，不排除聯合起來對中國產品採取報復性制裁措施，反擊中國屢次對澳洲的貿易打壓。澳洲昨日亦正式向世界貿易組織（WTO）申訴中國發動貿易戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳正式向世貿申訴<br />\n<br />\n澳洲新聞集團透露，五眼聯盟正在商議反制中國對澳洲進行貿易打壓，中國對澳洲出口商品的每一項制裁措施，先由安全機構進行聯合評估，若相關措施被認為「出於政治目的」向澳洲施壓，將實施報復性制裁。英國傳媒指目前五眼聯盟的官員們討論兩大辦法，其中一個是五個國家各自公佈對中國商品的制裁措施，另一方案是只由澳洲向中國實施懲罰性關稅，如果中國再有其他相動行動，四大盟國將支持澳洲，拒絕從中國入口相關產品。報道指有關計劃目前處談判階段，但在澳洲越來越受到重視，美方亦正在「認真考慮」。<br />\n<br />\n今年中澳關係不斷惡化，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》/澳洲新聞集團"},{"pid":"edd3807005b95fe29cbd9b77d1c6b5da0d85aedc","tid":2329412,"uid":244612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"249f2508b1a292ffd294c741f153fd03ca8d3622","tid":2329412,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:23:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201217/DK7Y7HGDGBHFTFVXLYERSNNTE4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201217%2FDK7Y7HGDGBHFTFVXLYERSNNTE4%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28Qpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=934d545f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201217%2FDK7Y7HGDGBHFTFVXLYERSNNTE4%2F&h=111d5375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201217/DK7Y7HGDGBHFTFVXLYERSNNTE4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華屢制裁澳貨 五眼聯盟擬報復<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FVZ7_XIwZhUwmWUDe-AeeQVtFa4=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F24QSOCRJJDMRKNNGB5KUWSVCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFVZ7_XIwZhUwmWUDe-AeeQVtFa4%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF24QSOCRJJDMRKNNGB5KUWSVCA.jpg&h=d9e7f913&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■澳洲正式向世貿控告中國發動貿易戰。<br />\n<br />\n中國近日不斷出招向澳洲貿易施壓，澳洲傳媒報道，由澳洲、新西蘭、美國、加拿大、英國組成的「五眼聯盟」正在商議一項計劃，不排除聯合起來對中國產品採取報復性制裁措施，反擊中國屢次對澳洲的貿易打壓。澳洲昨日亦正式向世界貿易組織（WTO）申訴中國發動貿易戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳正式向世貿申訴<br />\n<br />\n澳洲新聞集團透露，五眼聯盟正在商議反制中國對澳洲進行貿易打壓，中國對澳洲出口商品的每一項制裁措施，先由安全機構進行聯合評估，若相關措施被認為「出於政治目的」向澳洲施壓，將實施報復性制裁。英國傳媒指目前五眼聯盟的官員們討論兩大辦法，其中一個是五個國家各自公佈對中國商品的制裁措施，另一方案是只由澳洲向中國實施懲罰性關稅，如果中國再有其他相動行動，四大盟國將支持澳洲，拒絕從中國入口相關產品。報道指有關計劃目前處談判階段，但在澳洲越來越受到重視，美方亦正在「認真考慮」。<br />\n<br />\n今年中澳關係不斷惡化，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》/澳洲新聞集團"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:28:34.000Z","msg":"中華人民共和國世貿歷史（2000-2020）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7832dcbc0e2456f5b06c4a57dd96fe06e371efe6","tid":2329412,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:23:26.000Z","msg":"民主RUN得唔好可以好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n郁佢啦仲講"},{"pid":"c5369e861a9f0a53ba663773b06baa50916b4487","tid":2329412,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:26:04.000Z","msg":"如果聖誕節後開戰<br />\ntrump係咪可以唔退落黎然後廢埋支那燈個地位"},{"pid":"a2b3d2a28bf5be33ff797a6387843ce079e52ba5","tid":2329412,"uid":38982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:27:55.000Z","msg":"厲害了我的國, 一挑五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"799732c098f4e8e89e5292e6d1fbaee1c193fb51","tid":2329412,"uid":282637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVCfKsR.jpg&amp;h=620c3f80&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"442e4ed3966d83aaf0b9f232f6d1e9ddb23745c5","tid":2329412,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"799732c098f4e8e89e5292e6d1fbaee1c193fb51","tid":2329412,"uid":282637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVCfKsR.jpg&amp;h=620c3f80&amp;s=540\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:08:29.000Z","msg":"日本記者有時都幾幽默"},{"pid":"213046f0aa4ee7edb81244d1370f8b4fb453a623","tid":2329412,"uid":306340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"799732c098f4e8e89e5292e6d1fbaee1c193fb51","tid":2329412,"uid":282637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.